'''''Just Listen''''' is the first album by [[South Korea|Korean]] [[Pop music|pop]] and [[R&B]] singer [[Seven (South Korean singer)|Seven]], released on March 8, 2003, under [[YG Entertainment]]. It produced three singles: "<U+C640><U+C918>" (Come Back to Me), "<U+D55C><U+BC88> <U+B2E8> <U+D55C><U+BC88>" ("Once, Just Once") and "Baby I Like You Like That".

